    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>This is what we&#39;re having for dinner tonight. I&#39;ve made the sauce; it tasted great and is chilling in the fridge. But for people looking for plain Greek-style yogurt made from whole milk, hopefully you have a Trader Joe&#39;s nearby. Their whole milk Greek yogurt is substantially cheaper than their nonfat/lowfat versions, and it&#39;s almost as good as homemade. I&#39;m looking forward to tasting this pasta tonight. Thanks, Molly!</p>
