      <a href="https://orangette.net/2013/06/told-you-so/#comment-37798"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2013-07-05T00:00:40-04:00">Friday, July 5, 2013 at 12:00 am</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I DID make a half batch of this for dinner last night, using rotelli. It was excellent! I didn&#39;t have enough fresh peas for the entire dish, so I used thawed frozen peas for the puree. And I couldn&#39;t find my pine nuts in the freezer, so I substitued slivered almonds. But as much as I liked this last night, it was just as good as a chilled pasta salad for lunch. Definitely a keeper.</p>
    </div>

