      <p>You werent kidding about running. I was already infatuated with this book when I read about it in NYT recently. Now it&#39;s full on LUST. I made this recipe tonite for dinner. A few changes was substituting fresh mint for basil because I had it on hand. And I used chèvre instead of feta, and it got all melty and creamy. And for the more delicate palate i used 1/2 t. chile flakes. Amazing does not even begin to describe&#8230;</p>
